query.sfwSql: select SDBD.*, SCV.DESCRIPTION as istrBenefitOptionDescription, SCV.CODE_VALUE as istrBenefitOptionValue, SP.PLAN_CODE AS istrPlanCode, SP.PLAN_NAME AS istrPlanName from SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD WITH(NOLOCK) left outer JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDBD.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID left outer JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE SCV WITH(NOLOCK) ON SPBX.BENEFIT_OPTION_ID = SCV.CODE_ID AND SPBX.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE = SCV.CODE_VALUE join SGT_PLAN SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SP.PLAN_ID = SDBD.PLAN_ID WHERE DRO_APPLICATION_ID = @DRO_APPLICATION_ID
select count(*) from SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS where PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID and DRO_APPLICATION_ID = @DRO_APPLICATION_ID

SELECT SDA.ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID, SDBD.* FROM SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_PERSON SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SP.PERSON_ID = SDA.PERSON_ID join SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID join SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WITH(NOLOCK) ON spa.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID WHERE SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' AND SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) not in ('CMPL', 'CNCL')

SELECT SPA.*,sdbd.BENEFIT_FLAT_PERC,sdbd.BENEFIT_AMT from SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = SDBD.PLAN_ID JOIN SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' and (SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' OR (SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE <> 'STRF' AND SDA.DRO_COMMENCEMENT_DATE >= @BENEFIT_BEGIN_DATE )) AND SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL')

SELECT SPA.* ,SDBD.BENEFIT_PERC FROM SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WITH(NOLOCK) ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID join SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID join SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' AND SPBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 Q.* FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND Q.STATUS_VALUE = 'SPND' AND Q.SUSPENSION_STATUS_REASON_VALUE = 'REED' ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) AND SDBD.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID

SELECT sqco.*, sqcd.BENEFIT_SUBTYPE_VALUE, sqcd.alt_payee_ee_contribution, sqcd.ALT_PAYEE_MEMBER_EXCLUSION_AMOUNT,sqcd.ALT_PAYEE_AMT_BEFORE_CONVERSION, sqcd.FLAT_PERCENT, spbx.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE FROM SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_OPTIONS SQCO WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR spbx WITH(NOLOCK) ON SQCO.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = spbx.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID join SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL sqcd WITH(NOLOCK) ON sqcd.QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID = SQCO.QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID join SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER sqch WITH(NOLOCK) ON sqch.QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER_ID = sqcd.QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER_ID WHERE sqcd.QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID = @QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID

SELECT SPA.* ,SDBD.BENEFIT_PERC,SDBD.BENEFIT_FLAT_PERC,SDA.DRO_COMMENCEMENT_DATE FROM SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WITH(NOLOCK) ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID join SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID join SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL') AND (SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' OR (SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE <> 'STRF' AND SDA.IS_PARTICIPANT_DISABLED_FLAG = 'Y' and SDA.WAIVED_DISABILITY_ENTITLEMENT_FLAG = 'N' and SDA.DRO_COMMENCEMENT_DATE >= @BENEFIT_BEGIN_DATE )) AND SPBA.PERSON_ID <> SPA.PERSON_ID AND SPBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SDBD.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID

SELECT SPA.* ,SDBD.* FROM SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WITH(NOLOCK) ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID join SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID join SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL') AND SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' AND SPBA.PERSON_ID <> SPA.PERSON_ID AND SPBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SDBD.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE SDA.ELIGIBLE_FOR_CONTINUANCE_FLAG = 'Y' AND SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID = @DRO_BENEFIT_ID

select SPA.*,sdbd.BENEFIT_FLAT_PERC,sdbd.BENEFIT_AMT from SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = SDBD.PLAN_ID JOIN SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' and (SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE <> 'STRF' AND SDA.IS_PARTICIPANT_DISABLED_FLAG = 'Y' and SDA.WAIVED_DISABILITY_ENTITLEMENT_FLAG = 'N') AND SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL')

SELECT SPA.*,sdbd.BENEFIT_FLAT_PERC,sdbd.BENEFIT_AMT from SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = SDBD.PLAN_ID JOIN SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' and (SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' OR (SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE <> 'STRF' AND @BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE ='DSBL' AND SDA.DRO_COMMENCEMENT_DATE >= @BENEFIT_BEGIN_DATE )) AND SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL')
